// ====================== Stabilizer.sol ==============================
// ====================================================================
// Invests in off-chain & on-chain strategies
// Calculates junior / senior investment ratios
// Borrows freshly minted SWEEP for the senior tranche
// Repays debt by buying back SWEEP on paybacks and burns it
// Earns money charging a protocol spread sent to the treasury

// Primary Author(s)
// Max Coto: https://github.com/maxcoto

